🦄 Dropping some color on your feed. .
I took a few days off to get my mind right, and I strongly suggest if you also need one please take it. The shit will be here when you get back & hopefully the time away will give you the recharge & clarity that you need. Feeling like u have to keep up with the latest news, hottest tea, makeup releases & politics...on top of living your real life can be exhausting. I’m reminding myself that I did what I could with each day and there’s no reason to dwell on what I could have done better, or how I could more efficiently manage my time. It’s done & I’ll try to do better the next day. Now let’s get it this week. Happy Sunday fam 😛😘
